name: 𝐃𝐄𝐀𝐃 𝐄𝐍𝐃 Holiday Demo
description:
*
𝐃𝐄𝐀𝐃 𝐄𝐍𝐃 HOLIDAY MMXXII DEMO
For The Minicube64 fantasy console
*
Help Cliff, I mean... Santa find the presents for his beloved family, lost in Bridges Medical !
*

Run with minicube64 from commandline
Minicube64.exe path/deadend_holidaydemo_22122301.bin

Use arrow keys and Z to interact
*

𝐃𝐄𝐀𝐃 𝐄𝐍𝐃 is our in development stealth action adventure game inspired by Hideo Kojima games. This demo is a unique and separate experience from the finished game. We hope you enjoy it !

Minicube64 available from https://aeriform.itch.io/minicube64
